Motormaster flies towards base, and the way he is grumbling, you can almost
here his processor overheating from fury. He lands beside Astroblast, then
notices Killfest. He tries to compose himslef, but he is still visivly
upset, but Killfest's presence makes him cheer up a bit. "Well it is good
to see you my friend," He says, looking up at Killfest.


Wildrider:
Wildrider stands beside the Quintesson, who finally lifts himself from his
work, "There, it is done" He says, as he presses a button, and the newly
fixed Beastbox gets up. "Uhhhhh, Beastbox want to hurt something" he growl,
"Do it later" Wildrider responds, "I think I heard our grumpy leader" and
at that he hurries to get outside.
